text: Beniamino Mateinaqara (born 19 August 1987) is a Fijian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Lautoka in the Fijian National Football League. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:People from Taveuni Category:Fijian footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Fiji international footballers Category:Nadi F.C. players Category:Navua F.C. players Category:Hekari United players Category:Suva F.C. players Category:Lautoka F.C. players
